Phunky is Haml parser written in PHP

Example use:

<?php
require 'phunky.php';

$p = new Phunky($argv[1]);
$template = $p->compile();

$out = fopen("template.php", "w");
fwrite($out, $template);
fclose($out);

echo "========== template ==========\n";
echo $template;
echo "=========== result ===========\n";
require 'template.php';
?>
